data.description: Here is the perfect home for you. A brand new bathroom, much love and other updating makes this move in ready for you. Can't beat a great front porch and this house has a great enclosed front porch ready for you to sit and be indoors while enjoying the views of outside. The back has a patio that is semi-private for you to sit outdoors and enjoy the weather or entertaining. The nice corner lot boasts of alley access, a detached garage and yard shed. 2 bed and 1 bath on the main floor, full basement with a half bath and a great open space for a nice rec room. This is a must see. Call today for a private showing.
